These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, hamster, ferret, turtle
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, architect, analyst, photographer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, lacrosse, water-polo
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, lily, iris, dahlia
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 2. the person who growsdaisy is not to the left of the person who growsdaisy##8
 3. the person who growsdahlia is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
 5. the person who growsdaisy is not to the right of the person who growsdaisy##8
 6. the analyst is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
 8. the photographer is between the person who growslily and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 9. the person who growsdahlia is the analyst##1
10. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
11. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the dancer##3
12. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
13. the analyst is not to the left of the person who growsdahlia##8
14. the owner of the hamster is the person who growsiris##1
15. the owner of the hamster is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Pet         | lizard     | hamster   | turtle | ferret |
| Job   | architect | photographer   | dancer   | analyst  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey  | lacrosse  | water-polo  | cycling |
| Flower     | daisy    | iris | lily     | dahlia    |

