There are 4 different nationalities: indian, italian, indonesian, russian
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, librarian, paramedic, designer
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goldfish, rabbit
 1. the paramedic is between the owner of the dog and the librarian##2
 2. the aristoff-smoker is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
 3. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the indian##3
 4. the oliveros-smoker is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
 5. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the librarian##8
 6. the russian is not to the right of the dunhill-smoker##8
 7. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
 9. the scientist is the owner of the frog##1
10. the paramedic is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
11. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the paramedic##8
12. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
13. the designer is somewhere to the right of the italian##5
14. the librarian is on the left or right of the paramedic##3
15. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
16. the indonesian is on the right of the indian##1
17. the oliveros-smoker is not to the right of the librarian##8
18. the italian is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
19. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Cigar      | oliveros | baccarat | dunhill  | aristoff  |
| Nationality          | russian     | italian | indian | indonesian  |
| Job   | librarian    | paramedic  | designer | scientist |
| Pet           | goldfish | rabbit | dog    | frog  |

