.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, accountant, mechanic, writer
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, turtle, pony, dog
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, october, may, june
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, sailing, surfing
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the engineer##1
 2. the accountant is somewhere to the right of the mechanic##5
 3. the writer is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
 4. the mechanic is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
 6. the writer is not to the left of the owner of the pony##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
 8. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 9. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the far right##1
11. the owner of the rabbit is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##8
12. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job         | engineer    | writer   | mechanic | accountant |
| Pet   | rabbit     | pony  | dog   | turtle      |
| Birthday   | october | july    | may      | june       |
| Sport         | sailing    | climbing | surfing   | cycling    |

