.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, juice, tea, iced-tea
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, game, dunhill, davidoff
There are 4 different nationalities: british, malaysian, polish, russian
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, tomato, kale, artichoke
 1. the ritmeester-smoker is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
 2. the russian is the person drinking juice##1
 3. the person eating tomato is not the person drinking water##6
 4. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
 5. the ritmeester-smoker is not to the right of the polish##8
 6. the person eating kale is not to the right of the ritmeester-smoker##8
 7. the person eating tomato is not to the left of the person drinking juice##8
 8. the malaysian is the game-smoker##1
 9. the british is not to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##8
10. the dunhill-smoker is not to the left of the ritmeester-smoker##8
11. the person eating artichoke is between the person drinking iced-tea and the game-smoker##2
12. the person drinking water is on the right of the person eating kale##1
13. the malaysian is not to the right of the game-smoker##8
14. the person eating tomato is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage         | iced-tea     | water | tea   | juice  |
| Cigar   | davidoff | ritmeester   | game     | dunhill  |
| Nationality   | british    | polish     | malaysian | russian  |
| Food         | kale     | artichoke | blueberry   | tomato |

