 4. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to nizza##5
 5. the fan of salsa is the nigerian##1
 6. the person traveling to boston is not to the right of the dutch##8
 7. the person traveling to marseilles is not the thai##6
 8. the person watching sports movies is somewhere between the fan of salsa and the person traveling to marseilles##7
 9. the fan of salsa is somewhere to the right of the person watching sports movies##5
10. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
11. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
12. the person watching sports movies is not the argentine##6
13. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to marseilles##5
14. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
15. the fan of pop is not to the right of the person watching sports movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
