 4. the person who's hobby is chess is not the fan of dubstep##6
 5. the fan of d&b is not to the left of the fan of gospel##8
 6. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hannover##5
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 8. the person traveling to hamburg is not to the right of the person who likes yellow##8
 9. the fan of gospel is somewhere between the person traveling to hannover and the fan of reggae##7
10. the fan of gospel is not to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
11. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
12. the person who likes blue is not to the right of the fan of d&b##8
13. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
14. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
