.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, mirinda, water
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, time-travel, mystery, drama
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, pineapple, peas, plum
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, american, italian, polish
 1. the person drinking mirinda is the person eating plum##1
 2. the american is on the right of the polish##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 5. the mexican is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
 6. the italian is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
 8. the american is not to the right of the person eating pineapple##8
 9. the mexican is on the left of the person eating peas##1
10. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person watching time-travel movies##8
11. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person drinking water##1
12. the polish is in an odd position##4
13. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating pineapple##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | coffee   | water     | mirinda    | iced-tea |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | drama      | mystery     | time-travel     |
| Food         | cabbage | peas  | plum     | pineapple  |
| Nationality     | mexican     | italian | polish | american     |

