.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, may, december, july
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, chess, magic-tricks, skydiving
4 different pets are kept: goat, rat, lizard, guinea-pig
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, rugby, soccer, biathlon
 1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is the owner of the rat##1
 4. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the owner of the goat##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 8. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
 9. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
10. the owner of the lizard is not the person who's sport is volleyball##6
11. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
12. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
13. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
14. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |      4       |
| Birthday      | april      | july  | december | may        |
| Hobby         | skydiving | chess   | baking   | magic-tricks |
| Pet   | guinea-pig    | rat   | lizard    | goat      |
| Sport   | rugby   | biathlon | soccer   | volleyball    |

