.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, milk, sprite
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, swimming, tennis, weightlifting
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, collecting, singing, camping
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, daisy, sunflower, azalea
 1. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 2. the person who's hobby is camping is not to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##8
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
 6. the person who growsazalea is the person drinking juice##1
 7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the right of the person who growsazalea##8
 8. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
10. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
11. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##5
12. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
13. the person who growssunflower is not to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1        |    2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | juice          | iced-tea | milk        | sprite    |
| Sport         | weightlifting | parkour   | swimming | tennis  |
| Hobby         | singing           | cooking     | camping       | collecting  |
| Flower   | azalea            | sunflower   | daisy     | rose |

