.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, lemonade, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, d&b, pop, trance
4 different games are played: backgammon, domino, bridge, mah-jongg
4 different pets are kept: dog, bird, pony, lizard
 1. the fan of pop is not the person drinking lemonade##6
 2. the person playing backgammon is not to the left of the owner of the lizard##8
 3. the fan of trance is the owner of the bird##1
 4. the person playing backgammon is not to the left of the fan of d&b##8
 5. the person playing domino is somewhere to the right of the person playing bridge##5
 6. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the fan of trance is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
 8. the person drinking coffee is not to the left of the person playing bridge##8
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
10. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the owner of the lizard and the person playing mah-jongg##7
11. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |      2       |       3       |    4    |
| Beverage    | lemonade        | fanta        | coffee        | water   |
| Music-Genre       | d&b      | indie      | trance | pop |
| Game         | mah-jongg | bridge | domino     | backgammon  |
| Pet   | pony          | dog      | bird     | lizard  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, singing, sudoku
City: rome, liverpool, marseilles, paris
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, white, azure, ebony
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, german, polish, japanese
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person traveling to rome##8
 2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
 3. the japanese is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
 4. the person traveling to paris is the person who likes ebony##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is not the person traveling to marseilles##6
 6. the person who likes blood-red is not to the right of the german##8
 7. the person who likes white is not to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##8
 8. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is collecting##3
 9. the polish is in an even position##4
10. the person who likes blood-red is on the left or right of the german##3
11. the person who likes blood-red is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
13. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku    | singing   | board-games   | collecting |
| City           | rome | liverpool    | marseilles | paris    |
| Color   | azure   | blood-red | white     | ebony    |
| Nationality   | brazilian   | polish      | german         | japanese     |

 